HEADWORD: Bribeless
<hw>Bribe"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Incapable of being bribed; free
from bribes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>From thence to heaven's <qex>bribeless</qex> hall.</q>
<rj><qau>Sir W. Raleigh.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

